                    <p class="card-text">
                        Both teams gave their all, delivering a thrilling performance right until the final whistle."
                        "What an incredible display of skill and teamwork! The energy in the stadium was contagious."
                    </p>
                    <figcaption class="blockquote-footer mb-0 text-muted">
                        <cite title="Source Title">Tom Jeam</cite>
                    </figcaption>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card p-3">
                <figure class="p-3 mb-0">
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p>""Booking through the system was a breeze! I appreciated the clear event categories, and checkout was smooth. The event itself was fantastic, and I received my ticket instantly after booking. Highly recommended!""</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <figcaption class="blockquote-footer mb-0 text-muted">
                        <cite title="Source Title">Oliver W.</cite>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="~/images/workshop.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Your image description" width="100%" height="200">

                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Blues & Brew</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">I had some issues with booking initially, but customer support was quick to help. The event was amazing, and I loved that I could track all my bookings in one place. Will use this system again!</p>
