        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card bg-primary text-white text-center p-3">
                <figure class="mb-0">
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p>The user interface is very intuitive, and I found the event I wanted without any hassle. The detailed event descriptions and categories made it easier to decide. Definitely a great experience overall!</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <figcaption class="blockquote-footer mb-0 text-white">
                        <cite title="Source Title">Emma S</cite>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card text-center">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Enjoy The Fun</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">"I booked tickets for a theater show last minute, and everything went perfectly. The system was quick, and I appreciated the instant ticket delivery via email. Can’t wait for the next event!"</p>
                    <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted"> -Henry F.</small></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="~/images/music.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Your image description" width="100%" height="200">
                <figure class="mb-0">
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p>"The Country Roads Music Festival was a fantastic event! The performances were lively, and the atmosphere was warm and welcoming. The ticketing process was smooth, and I enjoyed every moment!"</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <figcaption class="blockquote-footer mb-0 text-muted">
                        <cite title="Source Title">  Michael K</cite>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card p-3 text-end">
                <figure class="mb-0">
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p>"The event selection was fantastic, and the platform was easy to navigate. I had no trouble finding events and booking tickets. The experience was great, and I’ll be back for more!"</p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <figcaption class="blockquote-footer mb-0 text-muted">
                        <cite title="Source Title"> Lily N.</cite>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Rock Legends Live</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">"Such a great platform for discovering new events! I found an amazing art exhibition and booking tickets was super easy. The confirmation was quick, and I had no issues at the venue. Will definitely use it again!"</p>
                    <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted"> -Alicia T. </small></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</main>



